{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be professional and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Designs</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0077b6;\n            --secondary-color: #90e0ef;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #03045e;\n            --card-background: #023e8a;\n            --button-hover-bg: #0096c7;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(3, 4, 94, 0.8), rgba(0, 119, 182, 0.8)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/03045e/0077b6?text=Design+Abstract') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            max-width: 800px;\n        }\n\n        #services .container {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-card {\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        .service-card i {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #portfolio .container {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .project-item {\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .project-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .project-overlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(3, 4, 94, 0.85);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;\n            padding: 20px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        .project-item:hover .project-overlay {\n            opacity: 1;\n        }\n\n        .project-overlay h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .project-overlay p {\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n        }\n\n        #contact .container {\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n        }\n\n        #contact h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        #contact p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            resize: vertical;\n            min-height: 150px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--button-hover-bg);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n\n            #hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2rem;\n            }\n\n            .service-card, .project-item {\n                min-width: unset;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Apex Designs</h1>\n            <p>Crafting Visual Excellence for Your Brand</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Innovative Design Solutions</h2>\n            <p>We transform ideas into compelling visual experiences that drive engagement and achieve your business goals.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-paint-brush\"></i>\n                <h3>Branding & Identity</h3>\n                <p>Creating memorable logos and comprehensive brand guidelines.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-object-group\"></i>\n                <h3>UI/UX Design</h3>\n                <p>Designing intuitive and user-friendly interfaces for web and mobile.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-bullhorn\"></i>\n                <h3>Marketing Materials</h3>\n                <p>Developing impactful graphics for campaigns and promotions.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Work</h2>\n            <div class=\"project-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/023e8a/ffffff?text=Project+One\" alt=\"Project One\">\n                <div class=\"project-overlay\">\n                    <h3>Project Alpha</h3>\n                    <p>A complete rebrand for a tech startup, focusing on modern aesthetics.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"project-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/023e8a/ffffff?text=Project+Two\" alt=\"Project Two\">\n                <div class=\"project-overlay\">\n                    <h3>Project Beta</h3>\n                    <p>Mobile app UI design for a health and wellness platform.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"project-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/023e8a/ffffff?text=Project+Three\" alt=\"Project Three\">\n                <div class=\"project-overlay\">\n                    <h3>Project Gamma</h3>\n                    <p>Branding and print design for a local artisanal bakery.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Let's Collaborate</h2>\n            <p>Have a project in mind? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Designs. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}